Not finding the service you need?
FL WINS Service Recommendations Just for You

You've taken the first step towards achieving your goals with FL WINS! We've analyzed your responses to our Service Match tool, and we're excited to share your personalized recommendations.

Check out your results by scanning the QR code or visiting the URL link below. Remember, these links are only active for 30 days.

Now, it's time to connect with services that can help you grow your career. You have two easy options:

A. Submit a registration intake form directly through the FL WINS portal

B. Visit a local career center, show them this email, and discuss your options with a case worker who can help you choose the best services for you.

We're looking forward to helping you acquire in-demand skills and boost your career. Let us know if you have any questions or need further assistance.

Best Regards,
The FL WINS Team
